### Security Rules (13 total)

| Priority | Rule | Pattern |
|----------|------|---------|
| 1 | sudo | `/\bsudo\b/i` |
| 2 | fork_bomb | `/:\s*\(\s*\)\s*:?\s*\{/` |
| 3 | backticks_rm | `/`[^`]*\brm\b[^`]*`/` |
| 3 | dollar_etc | `/\$\([^)]*\/etc\/[^)]*\)/` |
| 4 | su | `/\bsu\s+[-c]/` |
| 5 | system_deletion | `/\brm\s+(?:-[a-zA-Z]+\s+)?\/(?:etc\|usr\|bin\|sbin\|dev\|proc\|sys\|root)/` |
| 6 | recursive_root | `/\brm\s+-[a-zA-Z]*r[a-zA-Z]*\s+\/\s*(?:\|\|&\|$\|;)/` |
| 7 | dd_disk | `/\bdd\s+.*of=\s*\/dev\//i` |
| 7 | mkfs | `/\bmkfs\./i` |
| 7 | format | `/\bformat\s+/i` |
| 8 | wget_pipe | `/\|\s*.*\bwget\b/i` |
| 9 | device_redirect | `/[<>,&]\s*\/dev\/\w+/i` |
| 10 | chmod_system | `/\bchmod\s+.*\/+(etc\|usr\|bin\|sbin)\//i` |
| 10 | chown_system | `/\bchown\s+.*\/+(etc\|usr\|bin\|sbin)\//i` |
| 11 | symlink_root | `/\bln\s+[-fs].*\/root/i` |
| 12 | base64_decode | `/\bbase64\s+(?:-d\|--decode)\b/i` |
| 13 | exec_dev | `/\bexec\s+.*\/dev\//i` |
| 13 | exec_proc | `/\bexec\s+.*\/proc\//i` |

